\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Bridget and Liz both noticed Sarah unconsciously rubbing her pendant, prompting them to inquire about its significance. Surprised that Evan had never mentioned it to them, Sarah took the opportunity to share its backstory. Although usually a monotone storyteller, Sarah's narrative skills surprisingly elevated as she recounted the tale of how the jewelry was crafted and relived the emotional experience of receiving it from Evan on their first date.<!$Scr_Ps::4>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs18\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf6 <$Scr_Ps::3>Leading Context:<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::4>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Is Midway through Christmas Eve dinner. A host of subjects are being discussed in no particular order. This scene is simply switch from one topic to another.<!$Scr_Ps::4>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs18\b0\i0
